    <string name="sources_title">Text sources</string>
    <string name="sources_text">All texts are public domain: Westminster Leningrad Codex; Byzantine Textform 2018 (Robinson–Pierpont); Sanskrit NT 1851 (Calcutta Baptist Mission); Tamil IRV 2019; Vulgata Clementina 1592; Wycliffe; Tyndale; Geneva 1599; KJV with Apocrypha; Webster Bible 1833; Bible Martin 1744; Lutherbibel 1545; Karl XII:s Bibel 1703; Dansk Bibel 1819/1871; Statenvertaling 1637/1888; Reina-Valera 1909; Diodati 1649/1885; Bíblia Livre (Almeida, TR); 明治元訳 Meiji Motoyaku 1880/87; 和合本 Chinese Union 1919; Елизаветинская Библия 1757; Синодальный перевод. Webster\'s American Dictionary of the English Language (1828) via the 1828.mshaffer.com digitization. Strong\'s Concordance (1890/1894) dictionary © Open Scriptures, CC-BY-SA. Hebrew morphology © Open Scriptures (CC-BY); Greek parsing by Maurice A. Robinson (public domain). Cross-references © openbible.info, CC-BY. App text data via the scrollmapper, thiagobodruk, byztxt and Wikisource projects. Sanskrit NT digitization © SanskritBible.in, CC BY-SA 4.0. Tamil Indian Revised Version © Bridge Connectivity Solutions, CC BY-SA 4.0 (eBible.org). Latin text: The Clementine Vulgate Project (M. Tweedale et al.), public domain. Background music: Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com), CC BY 4.0.</string>
