    <string name="audio_title">Narrated audio (KJV)</string>
    <string name="audio_note">Human narration from LibriVox (public domain), covering most books of the KJV. Audio is downloaded per section (a few chapters, ~10–30 MB) when you press play and kept for offline listening. Books without a recording fall back to text-to-speech, and verse highlighting is unavailable while narrating.</string>
